column5: One of the local fisherman went out and caught this monster last Saturday from my favorite fishin spot. It was caught,transported, certified and released alive for future fun. This female on the next spawn will be over 90 lbs and a great addition to the genetics.       79 lb new Maryland state record  Art
Awesome fish  Thx for sharing that.
amazing, i bet that thing put up quite a fight ... thats one thing i love about those cats .. they love to fight/
wow, that thing is HUGE!!!  Glad to hear it was able to swim away ...  Maureen
One of these days! I have to take a trip down there! I'd love to bring up that sucker on a nice stiff Musky rod and baitcaster!
